{"tid":2096618,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【保就業】TVB申領8500多萬元，涉及3100多名僱員","createTime":"2020-07-06T08:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T11:43:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c809222c9e49d6aef70ae01c17072a668137a7","tid":2096618,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536059-20200706.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536059-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96Fo%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=23f16676\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536059-20200706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e2080aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536059-20200706.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n「保就業」計劃公布第三批僱主名單，涉及約3萬名僱主及逾33萬名受薪僱員，工資補貼額合共約77億元。<br />\n<br />\n有過百間獲批資助公司的承諾受薪僱員人數為0，部分公司申領金額超過10萬元，包括「聯向企業有限公司」、「時信專業服務有限公司」及「本草唯物」。<br />\n<br />\n至於申領最高金額的是「中原地產代理有限公司 」，涉及1億1500多萬元，承諾受薪僱員總數為5600多人；電視廣播有限公司申領8500多萬元，涉及3100多名僱員；美聯商業管理有限公司申領6300多萬元，涉及3100多名員工。<br />\n<br />\n零售業方面，周大福珠寶金行有限公司申領 7700多萬元，涉及2800多名員工；莎莎化妝品有限公司申領5900多萬元，承諾受薪僱員數目為2100多人。"},{"pid":"6fa7e5af7b7364c383ed47f411b09d0c48c7a24b","tid":2096618,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"識玩，求其幾百蚊個月既死約又當一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c39a2a4a1bce3ab7d6eeae4fe4bf4ff1d7050e","tid":2096618,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:50:51.000Z","msg":"全部國有化啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942a99befda16e26087b5128726ab9b24232d632","tid":2096618,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"TVB回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fro